<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="198" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[113,1089,219,532]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,243,251,275]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">Comments.</emphasis>
Based on the examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[602,648,252,276]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">type</typeStatus>
material, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Heyden" authorityYear="1877" box="[756,1089,253,276]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Mecynodera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">
<emphasis box="[756,1089,253,276]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">Mecynodera madagascariensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
fully corresponds with the generic characters of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1878" box="[624,757,285,308]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[624,757,285,308]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">Rhagiosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and I propose a new combination, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Heyden, 1877)" authorityName="Sekerka" authorityYear="2007" baseAuthorityName="Heyden" baseAuthorityYear="1877" box="[169,565,315,340]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariense" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[169,387,317,340]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">R. madagascariense</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON" box="[401,557,315,340]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" pagination="97 - 105" refId="ref4131" refString="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON 1877: Ueber die Kaferfauna von Madagaskar. Berichte der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft in Frankfurt a. M. 1877: 97 - 105." type="journal article" year="1877">Heyden, 1877</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[576,696,315,339]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
Thus, 
<taxonomicName authority="Chapuis, 1878" authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1878" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariense">
<emphasis box="[770,987,317,340]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">R. madagascariense</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="CHAPUIS F." pageId="3" pageNumber="198" refId="ref3878" refString="CHAPUIS F. 1878: Descriptions de deux genres noveaux de la famille des Phytophages. Comptes-Rendus de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 21: cxliii-cxlvii." type="book" year="1878">Chapuis, 1878</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, nec 
<bibRefCitation author="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON" box="[230,386,347,372]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" pagination="97 - 105" refId="ref4131" refString="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON 1877: Ueber die Kaferfauna von Madagaskar. Berichte der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft in Frankfurt a. M. 1877: 97 - 105." type="journal article" year="1877">Heyden, 1877</bibRefCitation>
, becomes its junior secondary homonym. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sekerka" authorityYear="2007" box="[855,1088,349,372]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chapuisi" status="nom. nov.">
<emphasis box="[855,1088,349,372]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">Rhagiosoma chapuisi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[113,219,380,403]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">nom. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is proposed here as a new substitute name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Chapuis, 1878" authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1878" box="[707,1085,379,404]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariense">
<emphasis box="[707,923,381,404]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">R. madagascariense</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="CHAPUIS F." box="[929,1085,379,404]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" refId="ref3878" refString="CHAPUIS F. 1878: Descriptions de deux genres noveaux de la famille des Phytophages. Comptes-Rendus de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 21: cxliii-cxlvii." type="book" year="1878">Chapuis, 1878</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, nec 
<bibRefCitation author="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON" box="[157,310,411,436]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" pagination="97 - 105" refId="ref4131" refString="HEYDEN L. F. J. D. VON 1877: Ueber die Kaferfauna von Madagaskar. Berichte der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft in Frankfurt a. M. 1877: 97 - 105." type="journal article" year="1877">Heyden, 1877</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[113,1089,219,532]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">
I found constant differences between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1878" box="[534,748,445,468]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariense">
<emphasis box="[534,748,445,468]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">R. madagascariense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sekerka" authorityYear="2007" box="[796,914,445,468]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chapuisi" status="nom. nov.">
<emphasis box="[796,914,445,468]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">R. chapuisi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[919,1024,444,467]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">nom. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
based on the study of the 
<typeStatus box="[321,367,476,500]" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">type</typeStatus>
material. Differential diagnosis and additional comments are given under 
<emphasis box="[181,404,509,532]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1878" box="[181,400,509,532]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Rhagiosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariense">R. madagascariense</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
